snippet.title: Mon-Yu - Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: Check out gameplay, character classes, combat, and more in this trailer for Mon-Yu, an upcoming dungeon crawler available on PlayStation 5, Nintendo Switch, and PC on September 21, 2023.
